'''ANX国际'''（{{lang-en|'''ANX INTERNATIONAL'''}}）是一家香港[[区块链|区块链]]技术的[[金融科技|金融科技]]公司，[[香港區塊鏈協會|香港區塊鏈協會]]會員，成立于2013年6月。于2014年2月，ANX国际于香港西环成立全球首家比特币交易实体店；<ref>{{cite news | work=凤凰财经 | title=比特币香港实体店开业 | first=品瑜 | last=岳 | date=2014-03-03 | url=http://finance.ifeng.com/a/20140303/11789928_0.shtml | accessdate=2016-05-24 | archive-date=2016-06-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160624155804/http://finance.ifeng.com/a/20140303/11789928_0.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>于2014年3月，开设全球首家支持多种货币交易的在线比特币交易平台，同时推出了全球第三台比特币自动柜员机以及移动手机应用程序ANX数字钱包（ANX Vault）；<ref>{{cite news | work=SCMP | title=香港ANX宣布其平台已添加网络黄金EGD交易 | date=2015-02-12 | url=http://finance.china.com/fin/kj/201502/12/0221843.html | access-date=2016-05-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160605140808/http://finance.china.com/fin/kj/201502/12/0221843.html | archive-date=2016-06-05 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>于2014年7月，ANX国际推出全球首张数字资产签账金融卡；<ref>{{cite news | work=凤凰财经 | title=比特币首次嵌入银行支付系统 拓展B2B清算 | date=2014-07-23 | url=http://finance.ifeng.com/a/20140723/12774746_0.shtml | accessdate=2016-05-24 | archive-date=2016-06-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160624154655/http://finance.ifeng.com/a/20140723/12774746_0.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>于2016年5月，在香港亚太科技博览大会上，ANX国际推出全球首个免费即时区块链应用平台。<ref>{{cite news | work=中国日报 | title=ANX推出全球首个免费即时区块链应用定制平台 | date=2016-05-23 | url=http://caijing.chinadaily.com.cn/2016-05/23/content_25428245.htm | accessdate=2016-05-24 | archive-date=2016-06-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160623233304/http://caijing.chinadaily.com.cn/2016-05/23/content_25428245.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>2021年8月30日结业。{{CN}}

== 公司历史 ==
* ANX国际成立于2013年6月17日，由卢建邦，Dave Chapman，Hugh Madden联合创立。
* 于2014年2月28日，ANX国际在香港西营盘成立全球首家比特币交易实体店，支持比特币和港币之间的兑换。<ref>{{cite news|title=A Look at the World's First Bitcoin Shop|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/b/26f7d7f0-50f9-4054-b9be-27fe2c49cd3a|accessdate=1 June 2015|agency=Bloomberg|date=28 February 2014|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117030716/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/b/26f7d7f0-50f9-4054-b9be-27fe2c49cd3a|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Bitcoin ATMs Open in Singapore|url=http://blogs.wsj.com/digits/2014/02/28/bitcoin-atms-open-in-singapore/|accessdate=1 June 2015|agency=The Wall Street Journal|date=28 February 2014|archive-date=2016-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160318173707/http://blogs.wsj.com/digits/2014/02/28/bitcoin-atms-open-in-singapore/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title='World's first' Bitcoin shop opens doors in Hong Kong|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/breaking-news/money/story/worlds-first-bitcoin-shop-opens-doors-hong-kong-20140228|accessdate=26 May 2015|publisher=THE STRAITS TIMES|date=28 February 2015|archive-date=2015-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150526141720/http://www.straitstimes.com/breaking-news/money/story/worlds-first-bitcoin-shop-opens-doors-hong-kong-20140228|dead-url=no}}</ref> 这标志着ANX国际成为线上线下兼备的数字交易平台。<ref>{{cite news|title=Bitcoin exchange opens in Hong Kong|url=http://edition.cnn.com/videos/business/2014/03/03/intv-stevens-ken-lo-bitcoin.cnn|accessdate=1 June 2015|agency=CNN|date=3 March 2014|archive-date=2016-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160702051059/http://edition.cnn.com/videos/business/2014/03/03/intv-stevens-ken-lo-bitcoin.cnn|dead-url=no}}</ref> 
* 于2014年3月13日，ANX国际宣布推出全港首台、全球第三台比特币自动柜员机。<ref>{{cite news|title=Hong Kong Company Launches City's First Bitcoin ATM|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/hong-kong-company-launches-citys-first-bitcoin-atm-10743|website=International Business Times|accessdate=1 June 2015|archive-date=2016-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160410142725/http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/hong-kong-company-launches-citys-first-bitcoin-atm-10743|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="South China Morning Post">{{cite news|title=Three companies set to launch bitcoin ATMs in Hong Kong within days|url=http://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/article/1448009/three-companies-set-launch-bitcoin-atms-hong-kong-within-days|accessdate=26 May 2015|agency=Christy Choi|publisher=South China Morning Post|date=14 March 2014|archive-date=2016-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160516213202/http://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/article/1448009/three-companies-set-launch-bitcoin-atms-hong-kong-within-days|dead-url=no}}</ref> 该自动柜员机支持比特币和港币之间的兑换。
* 于2014年7月，ANX国际推出全球首张数字资产签账金融卡。该金融卡支持商户在全球范围内通过自动柜员机提取当地货币。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.coindesk.com/exchange-anx-launch-reloadable-bitcoin-debit-cards/|title = Hong Kong Exchange ANX Launches Bitcoin Debit Card|date = July 15, 2014|accessdate = May 30, 2015|website = CoinDesk|publisher = |last = |first = |archive-date = 2016-07-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160708001144/http://www.coindesk.com/exchange-anx-launch-reloadable-bitcoin-debit-cards/|dead-url = no}}</ref>
* 于2016年5月18日，在亚洲国际博览馆举行的「香港亚太云端科技博览会」上，ANX国际推出全球首个区块链技术云端平台，免费让全球企业使用。该云端平台上的区块链技术应用包括：将传统资产转化成数字资产、建立资料库、电子钱包服务、以及资产交易平台。<ref>{{cite news | work=明报 | title=ANX推区块链云端免费平台 | date=2016-05-18 | url=http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20160518/s00004/1463508470772 | accessdate=2016-05-25 | archive-date=2016-05-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160519114429/http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20160518/s00004/1463508470772 | dead-url=no }}</ref>
* 從2019年6月1日開始進入維護狀態，所有交易服務停止。<ref>{{cite web |title=ANXPRO公告 |date=2019-10-30 |url=https://anxpro.com/stories/announcements |accessdate=2019-10-30 |archive-date=2019-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190812072150/https://anxpro.com/stories/announcements |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 收购记录 ==
=== Justcoin ===
于2014年11月，ANX国际收购了挪威比特币交易公司Justcoin，进一步扩张其欧洲数字货币交易的市场份额。<ref>{{cite web|title=Bitcoin Weekly 2015 January 28: All about exchange-Winklevoss Gemini, Coinbase Exchange, CoinMkt|url=http://siliconangle.com/blog/2015/01/28/bitcoin-weekly-2015-january-28-all-about-exchanges-winklevoss-gemini-coinbase-exchange-coinmkt/|website=siliconANGLE|accessdate=10 July 2015|archive-date=2016-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160730045133/http://siliconangle.com/blog/2015/01/28/bitcoin-weekly-2015-january-28-all-about-exchanges-winklevoss-gemini-coinbase-exchange-coinmkt/|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref name="THE COINTELEGRAPH">{{cite news|title=ANX Acquires Justcoin, Incorporates Platform within a Week|url=http://cointelegraph.com/news/112963/anx-acquires-justcoin-incorporates-platform-within-a-week|accessdate=27 May 2015|agency=William Suberg|publisher=THE COINTELEGRAPH|date=21 November 2014|archive-date=2015-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150711125924/http://cointelegraph.com/news/112963/anx-acquires-justcoin-incorporates-platform-within-a-week|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== CoinMkt ===
于2015年1月，ANX国际收购了美国加密货币交易公司CoinMkt，进一步扩张其美国数字货币交易的市场份额。
<ref name="forexminute.com">{{cite web|title=Bitcoin Company ANXBTC Acquires Santa Monica-based exchange West Orange Labs, Inc|url=http://www.forexminute.com/bitcoin/bitcoin-company-anxbtc-acquires-santa-monica-based-exchange-west-orange-labs-inc-54059|website=FareXMinute|accessdate=10 July 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924014606/http://www.forexminute.com/bitcoin/bitcoin-company-anxbtc-acquires-santa-monica-based-exchange-west-orange-labs-inc-54059|archivedate=2015年9月24日}}</ref> 并购后，CoinMkt将维持本品牌的独立营运，但将会归列于ANX国际的集团之内。<ref>{{cite web|title=Bitcoin Weekly 2015 January 28: All about exchanges- Winklevoss Gemini, Coinbase Exchange, CoinMkt|url=http://siliconangle.com/blog/2015/01/28/bitcoin-weekly-2015-january-28-all-about-exchanges-winklevoss-gemini-coinbase-exchange-coinmkt/|website=siliconANGLE|accessdate=10 July 2015|archive-date=2016-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160730045133/http://siliconangle.com/blog/2015/01/28/bitcoin-weekly-2015-january-28-all-about-exchanges-winklevoss-gemini-coinbase-exchange-coinmkt/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

